   NETHAWAY-COLUMN _ WACO, Texas _ If Patrick Joseph Buchanan isn't
a racist, fascist and bigot, then he needs to stop imitating those
traits. (Nethaway, Waco Tribune-Herald) MOVED.
</P>
<P>
   KELSO-COLUMN _ AUSTIN, Texas _ Is there any group outside of an
elementary school swing set who can whine as spectacularly and
annoyingly as the British? What a bunch of crybabies. The British
media got their noses out of joint because the Americans _ wives,
caddies, fans _ ran onto the green before Spain's Jose Maria
Olazabal could putt. But to hear the Brits howl about it, you would
have thought the Americans had mooned Buckingham Palace. Which is a
pretty good idea because it would make for a great European
vacation slide. (Kelso, Austin American-Statesman) MOVED.
</P>
