Istriano, Bruno Viscovi's grandmother prepared chifeleti, which he
characterizes as a type of gnocchi, when he was growing up in
Albona on the Istrian Peninsula in Italy. The dish is accompanied
by beef sirloin sauce flavored with cumin.
