<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-09-29 15:58 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A0406 &Cx1f; ttf-z
u v BC-PAGEEXPRESS-BUDGET-UP     09-29 0298
</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-PAGEEXPRESS-BUDGET-UPDATE-NYTSF </SLUG>
 
<TEXT>
<P>
   Here is an updated budget for the Wrestling and Nascar Pages.
