<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-09-29 16:44 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A0455 &Cx1f; taf-z
u l BC-HOME-IMPROVEMENT-ART-     09-29 0758
