   FOOTBALL/COLLEGES
</P>
<P>
   FBC-BARNHART _ Inside College Football column by Atlanta
Journal-Constitution columnist Tony Barnhart. (Barnhart, Atlanta
Journal-Constitution). 18.
</P>
<P>
   FBC-GATECH _ ATLANTA _ Advance for Thursday's Georgia Tech vs.
Maryland game. (Clemons, Atlanta Journal-Constitution). 14.
</P>
<P>
   FBC-VOLS-ESPN _ Tennessee fans think think the world - or at
least ESPN - is out to get them in the wake of the network's report
on possible academic fraud in the program. A Web site connected to
the Knoxville paper is conducting a poll asking if ESPN is out to
