came out with money and good will to help Danube Elementary School
in Granada Hills after the Northridge Earthquake. Now the Granada
Hills school is returning the goodwill with donations to Tarboro
students whose community was deluged by Hurricane Floyd. By Dennis
McCarthy. (Will move in the ``n'' California and ``a'' national
news file.)
