speech at the Ronald Reagan Presidential Library on Wednesday. In a
year when a lot of Republican contenders are vying for the title of
Ronald Reagan's spiritual heir, John McCain may have snatched the
biggest prize of all: the tacit endorsement of Nancy Reagan.
(Monica Almeida/New York Times Photo)
