CIR-SWAN-GIRLS-2, 09-29 -- The Bug 'Em remote listening device by
Girl Tech. Want more ideas? At 41, Janese Swanson, the company's
founder, has a million of them. But unlike countless other mothers
who fantasize about creating whine-stopping diversions for their
children, she sees some of her ideas hit the market. (Thor
Swift/New York Times Photo)
