the Brooklyn Museum, ``dung happens.'')
</P>
<P>
   The museum's serenely elitist board members are either
incredibly stupid or knew _ and did not care _ that this would (a)
offend the religious, (b) anger and divide the city, (c) make a ton
of money for the exhibition's owners, and (d) make the museum's
