<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-BIZMAGS30-COX </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
&HT;   
</HEADLINE>
 &HT;    Warm-up starts for millennial finish
 &HT;    By Tom Walker
 &HT;    c.1999 Cox News Service
<TEXT>
<P>
   ATLANTA _ Major magazines are anticipating the millennium with
special editions that usually look at past achievements and ahead
to what the experts think life in the 21st century will be like.
</P>
